snippet.title: Onlydraven Gaming
snippet.description:
My name is Onlydraven and I make video content that is designed to entertain and educate.  I play many different games but primarily Minecraft and the different mods that can be combined with it.

I create short, easy to follow tutorials showing the many types of blocks, mechanics and combinations found within Minecraft, as well as Live Gaming Streams and Let's Play style videos.  I also am a long time Dungeons & Dragons player/DM who has been writing and running the same campaign/storyline for 30 years, which I share on stream under the name Mergedworlds, which is also available as an audio podcast on iTunes and Spotify.

Currently I release videos throughout the week.  For my streaming schedule, my PC specs and other useful information, please visit www.onlydraven.com.

Gaming Off the Grid focuses on gaming together with friends, offline. This new channel offers high quality weekly content that covers a wide array of gaming topics and reviews a new beer in every upload. From the retro gaming to the modern gaming scene, this channel has you covered. This tag team brings their high energy and passion to every episode. So, sit back, relax, pour yourself a beer if you care to and welcome to Gaming Off the Grid.

I create tech & gaming oriented content- PC gaming, Console gaming PS3, PS4, PS5, PS2, XBOX 360, XBOX ONE/ONE S, XBOX SERIES . gaming consoles.
I test different video game titles in a POV (point of view) style of shooting. This creates a more immersive experience for the viewers. 
I really enjoy the process of making these videos. Although it takes a lot of my  time. Typically the making of a single video takes about 1-2 days , including planning, capturing the footage, editing, uploading, writing a compelling description, thumbnail. 

I enjoy every second of that process. I read all your comments and i try to improve myself in every new video.

snippet.title: Three Sails Studios
snippet.description:
Three Sails Studios is a tabletop miniature wargames publisher, (soon-to-be) manufacturer, and a design consultancy, based in Manchester, UK.

MARGRAVE: THE MARCHER LORDS is our first game, designed in-house by George Francis Bickers (who also hosts this channel!). A rank-and-flank tabletop miniature wargame, complete with a range of beautifully sculpted and highly detailed 32mm miniatures, Margrave will be releasing on crowdfunding platforms in September 2023.

Come and join us on this new journey as we build Three Sails Studios into a fully-fledged publishing company, manufacturer, and design studio.

www.threesailsstudios.com
www.margravethemarcherlords.com
